doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    title URL Shortener Microservice
    link(href='/bootstrap.min.css', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
    link(href='/app.css', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
  body
   div.container.backdrop
    h1.text-center URL Shortener Microservice
    h3 User stories:
    ol
     li I can pass a URL as a parameter and I will receive a shortened URL in the JSON response.
     li When I visit that shortened URL, it will redirect me to my original link.

    h2 Example creation usage:
    p.
      #{url}new/https://www.google.com <br />
     #{url}new/http://foo.com:80

    h2 Example creation output:
    p { "original_url":"http://foo.com:80", "short_url":"#{url}8170" }

    h2 Usage:
    p.
      #{url}2871   will be directed to https://www.google.com/
